    <description>Plan-first S3 object storage migration and sync CLI. Resumable, observable
      migrations for large S3-compatible object storage. Supports S3-to-S3, local-to-S3, and
      S3-to-local transfers.

      NOTE: This is commercial software. A permanent free tier (10 GB per run, no registration
      required) is included. Register a free account at https://godwit.io to get a 30-day trial
      license with 50 GB per run — no credit card required. Paid plans start at €15/month. See
      https://godwit.io/pricing for details.</description>
